# ── solve guides ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Per-chapter READMEs are instructor notes with reference payloads and
# step-by-step walkthroughs. They must not ship to the public repo.
# The top-level README.md is descriptive only and is intentionally tracked.
vulns/*/README.md

# ── runtime state ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SQLite DB and on-disk lab files are recreated on startup; nothing here
# should ever be committed.
practica.db
labdata/

# ── personal notes ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
solves.txt
NOTES.md
notes.md

# ── build artifacts ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/practicabitapp
*.exe
*.test
*.out
coverage.txt

# ── editor / OS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
